 <PERSON> Marcos </PERSON>' daughter <PERSON> Irene </PERSON>. It was hoped the resort and its casino would attract high rollers from <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION> and Filipino immigrant families from the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> wishing to vacation in their homeland. Last week, the hotel had only three guests.
